		<description>MaulingMonKey's Json Writer API.  No, the world didn't really need another JSON writer library.  Yes, I wrote one anyways.

Project Goals:
- Zero Allocations - I should be able to use this to report heap corruptions.  Payload limits are a feature (tm).
- Cross Platform - any C++03 compiler should work (tm).
- Less Bugs - via the abuse of macros &amp; variable shadowing, to avoid common errors.
- No Config - aiming to have "perfect" NuGet integration, with .libs, sane defaults, and source compilation fallback.</description>
